Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.47,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.00,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku Komura Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:12.02,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Aku nyaris telat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.44,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Semoga bisa tepat waktu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:20.69,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mi-Mie-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:27.37,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Walau telat berangkat begini, tapi aku senang bisa berangkat bersamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.28,0:04:32.12,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Pa-Pagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:35.21,Miring,Mie,0,0,0,,Se-Selamat pagi!
