Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.64,Utama,Azuma,0,0,0,,Mie-san, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.64,0:06:26.40,Utama,Azuma,0,0,0,,Komura-kun, gendong di ke UKS!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.30,0:06:29.52,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Azuma-kun kenapa, sih?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:32.37,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Apa dia mendukungku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.87,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Bukan hanya wajahnya,\N tapi sekujur tubuhnya dekat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.41,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mie-san deket banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:42.88,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mie-san pasti tidak grogi dalam situasi seperti ini, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.48,0:06:46.64,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.34,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Maaf kalau aku berat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:53.35,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Akhir-akhir ini aku sedikit gendutan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:56.85,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Dia mengkhawatirkan berat badannya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.36,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Imutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.78,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,I-Imutnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:09.68,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Mau beratmu puluhan atau bahkan ratusan kilo,\Naku tidak masalah!
