Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.26,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Komura-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:22.02,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Guru memintaku mengganti kertas pengumuman di papan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.42,Miring,Komura,0,0,0,,Guru sialan!
