Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.91,Utama,Mie,0,0,0,,Tanganku nyaris enggak nyampai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.86,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Baiklah, Mie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:33.15,Utama,Komura,0,0,0,,Biar aku lepaskan ....
